  "genus": "Ganoderma",
  "description": {
    "en": "The spores of Ganoderma lucidum, the reproductive cells produced by the fruiting body. Spores are a distinct life stage from the fruiting body (Reishi/Lingzhi) and have different therapeutic properties and bioavailability.",
    "zh-Hant": "野生靈芝孢子是靈芝（學名：Ganoderma lucidum）的生殖細胞，由子實體產生。孢子與子實體（靈芝）是不同的生命階段，具有不同的藥理特性和生物利用度。",
    "zh-Hans": "野生灵芝孢子是灵芝（学名：Ganoderma lucidum）的生殖细胞，由子实体产生。孢子与子实体（灵芝）是不同的生命阶段，具有不同的药理特性和生物利用度。"
  },
